DESCRIPTION:Join us on Wednesday\, March 25th from 4–7 PM at Whispering Vine South Creek for a fun and easygoing tasting featuring the crowd-pleasing wines of JaM Cellars Butter. From bold reds to bright whites\, this lineup highlights rich California flavors and approachable styles made for everyday enjoyment.\nTasting Fee: $10 (Buy a bottle from the tasting and your fee is refunded)\nFeatured Wines:\n- JaM Cellars Butter Cabernet Sauvignon – Smooth and juicy with dark red fruit\, soft oak\, and a touch of vanilla on the lingering finish.\n- JaM Cellars Butter Pinot Noir – Bright and silky with ripe strawberry\, Bing cherry\, and subtle vanilla spice.\n- JaM Cellars Butter Chardonnay – Rich and creamy with stone fruit\, baked lemon\, and a long\, luscious vanilla finish.\n- JaM Cellars Butter Sauvignon Blanc – Refreshing and tropical with key lime\, pineapple\, papaya\, and a crisp\, clean finish.\nDiscover why Butter wines are such a fan favorite—buy a bottle and your tasting is free.
LOCATION:85 Foothill Rd Ste 1 Reno\, NV 89511
SUMMARY:Butter Tasting
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR